# Wine Price Prediction - Environment Variables
# Add these in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables

# Z.AI API Key (free tier) - powers wine search and label scanning
# Get one at: https://open.bigmodel.cn/
ZAI_API_KEY=

# Google Gemini API Key (optional fallback for label scanning)
# Get one at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=
